                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-16-off87 t18180218-16-cd88"></join>, one book, value 4s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18180218-16-victim134" type="victimName">
                  Edward 
